        "content_en": "The internet is a vast resource for solving problems. If you encounter an issue, search for it on Google or YouTube. For example, if your phone's Wi-Fi isn't connecting, search 'phone Wi-Fi not connecting' on Google. You'll likely find step-by-step guides or video tutorials. Practice this: open your web browser, go to Google.com, and search for 'How to clear cache on Android phone' or 'How to clear cache on iPhone'. Watch one of the short YouTube videos that appear as a result.",
